# Last matching rule per file wins. Approval from any listed owner satisfies
# the requirement. quickwit-core is listed on every rule so it can always
# approve; byoc-metrics is added on metrics-specific paths so PRs scoped to
# those paths can be approved by either team.

# Default: quickwit-core owns everything
